<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Hudaco lifts year headline shr, div.</title>
<headline>Hudaco lifts year headline shr, div.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-01-21</dateline>
<text>
<p>Year ended November 30</p>
<p>			(million rand unless stated)</p>
<p>    Headline shr (cts)    206.0	 vs 180.0</p>
<p>    Div (cts)		 90.0	  vs 80.0</p>
<p>    Headline earnings     60.9	  vs 51.9</p>
<p>    Attrib income	   65.7	  vs 50.0</p>
<p>    Pre-tax		   89.4	  vs 77.7</p>
<p>    Tax			 25.8	  vs 21.4</p>
<p>    Net finance costs     16.0	  vs 1.9</p>
<p>Turnover</p>
<p>    - ongoing operations  1,088.0     vs 709.5</p>
<p>Div payable March 24</p>
<p>on register February 28</p>
<p>Full name: Hudaco Industries Ltd</p>
<p>    Exceptional items     5.3 loss    vs 2.5 loss</p>
<p>NOTE - Directors said the exceptional loss related to the sale of operations. They said barring any further slowdown in the company's markets, it should increase its earnings per share in real terms in the current financial year.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
